OL,6,FThere was a breakdown on the BBC      
OL,7,FScotland Channel shortly after 9.25pm 
OL,8,Ftonight, when live coverage of the    
OL,9,FHearts v FC Zurich match was          
OL,10,Finterrupted due to "satellite issues".
OL,12,FThe breakdown lasted over ten minutes.
OL,13,FPrior to the appearance of the        
OL,14,Fbreakdown slide, there was a few      
OL,15,Fminutes or so of largely frozen       
OL,16,Fpicture/sound, with brief flashes of  
OL,17,Fblack screen (though we're told the   
OL,18,Fblack flashes were unique to BBC      
OL,19,FiPlayer).                             
OL,3,CBBC Scotland Channel loses live       
OL,4,Cfootball for over ten minutes         
OL,22,                                   G1/3
