OL,6,FDuring the short periods of black on  
OL,7,FiPlayer, the channel DOG also         
OL,8,Fdisappeared.                          
OL,10,FThe breakdown slide was accompanied by
OL,11,Fbirdsong. Audio from BBC Radio Scotland
OL,12,Fcoverage of the match might've been a 
OL,13,Fmore suitable substitute.             
OL,15,FJust prior to returning to the live   
OL,16,Ffootball, there were more brief flashes
OL,17,Fof black, interrupting the breakdown  
OL,18,Fcaption. Again the black flashes were,
OL,19,Fapparently, on the BBC iPlayer only.  
OL,3,CBBC Scotland Channel loses live       
OL,4,Cfootball for over ten minutes         
