OL,6,FRepeated black flashes also caused the
OL,7,FiPlayer to crash out of the live stream
OL,8,Fon a number of occasions during the   
OL,9,Fperiod affected by the satellite      
OL,10,Fproblem.                              
OL,12,FAnd there were some gremlins with the 
OL,13,Fon-screen scorecard near the end of   
OL,14,Ftonight's match. When the extra time  
OL,15,Felement was added to the on-screen    
OL,16,Ftimer, FC Zurich lost their goal. It  
OL,17,Fwas reinstated about and              
OL,18,Fminute-and-a-half later.              
